These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, fisherman, journalist
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, cranberry, pepper
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, lily
3 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, hamster
1. the person eating cranberry is the fisherman##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
3. the journalist is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the journalist is the person eating pepper##1
7. the person who growslily is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Job      | journalist  | social-worker       | fisherman   |
| Food          | pepper | cauliflower | cranberry |
| Flower         | marigold  | lily | aconite    |
| Pet   | hamster | bird       | rabbit      |

