.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, designer, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, swimming, handball
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, april
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, snake
1. the photographer is on the left of the designer##1
2. the police-officer is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Job          | photographer      | designer  | police-officer        |
| Sport         | handball | swimming | rowing |
| Birthday   | march | february | april       |
| Pet           | snake     | rat     | hedgehog      |

