.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
City: new-york, venice, london
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, cain, old-henry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, indian, indonesian
1. the old-henry-smoker is the pakistani##1
2. the indian is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the cain-smoker is on the left of the pakistani##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| City      | venice    | new-york        | london |
| Cigar           | cain    | old-henry | davidoff    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie             | satire  |
| Nationality     | indonesian     | pakistani                | indian  |

