.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, biathlon
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, lawyer
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, light-blue, emerald
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, tram, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the bus##1
5. the person who likes red is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Sport          | lacrosse    | biathlon  | cricket      |
| Job           | lawyer    | analyst | fisherman |
| Color   | emerald   | light-blue  | red     |
| Transport   | bike | tram    | bus      |

