.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, singing, video-games
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bongani, siglo
There 3 different types of food: pepper, lemon, lettuce
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, yellow, white
1. the person eating pepper is the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the siglo-smoker is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes ivory is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person eating lettuce is the swisher-smoker##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking     | singing   |
| Cigar           | siglo       | bongani   | swisher     |
| Food   | lemon     | pepper | lettuce |
| Color           | white      | ivory         | yellow  |

