The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
3. the farmhouse house is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
6. the cottage house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| House       | farmhouse            | futuristic      | cottage  |
| Flower         | zinnia | dahlia | iris |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate               | lemonade | sprite |
| Transport   | roller             | ship       | bus      |

