.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, orange, lavender
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, mystery
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, dubstep, pop
3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, chess
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes black is on the left of the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Color           | lavender | black         | orange |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | martial-arts | mystery     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | dubstep       | pop     |
| Game           | chess    | billiard         | backgammon        |

