2. the coralcher is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the person who likes coral is the prince-smoker##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is the person who likes turquise##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Color      | turquise         | coral     | light-blue     |
| Job           | lawyer        | coralcher | journalist |
| Flower   | marigold        | poppy   | balloon-flower    |
| Cigar         | montecristo | prince   | bolivar |

