.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy, zinnia
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, traveling
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, superhero, satire
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, boat, roller
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Flower          | zinnia     | daisy    | orchid    |
| Hobby         | collecting | traveling | hiking     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | superhero      | satire        |
| Transport         | van   | boat   | roller |

 